      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is Microsoft Copilot worth $30/month for a small business?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Only if your whole team uses Microsoft 365. Copilot is great inside Outlook and Excel but useless if you're on Google Workspace. At $30/user/month, it's the priciest option here—make sure you'll actually use it daily."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can AI tools actually save time for a solo business owner?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, but some save way more than others. ChatGPT Team saved me about 45 minutes per day on email and brainstorming. Canva AI saved about 2 hours per week on graphics. Zapier AI? Barely 15 minutes a day because setting up automations took longer than doing things by hand for a solo operation."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which AI business tool has the best free plan?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "ChatGPT's free tier gives you GPT-4o, which handles most small business writing tasks. HubSpot's free CRM includes basic AI for contact management. Canva's free tier has some AI features but limits exports. Start with ChatGPT Free if budget is tight."
      }
